## Example 2 — Add Polynomials

Find:

`(6x^3 + 7x^2 - 2x + 5) + (x^3 - 4x^2 - 8x + 1)`

### Method 1: Add horizontally

`(6x^3 + x^3) + (7x^2 - 4x^2) + (-2x - 8x) + (5 + 1)`

`= 7x^3 + 3x^2 - 10x + 6`

### Method 2: Add vertically

```
  6x^3 + 7x^2 - 2x + 5
+   x^3 - 4x^2 - 8x + 1
-----------------------
  7x^3 + 3x^2 - 10x + 6
```

---

## Example 3 — Subtract Polynomials

Find:

`(2x^5 + 11x^4 + 7x - 8) - (5x^4 + 9x^3 - 3x + 4)`

### Method 1: Subtract horizontally

`2x^5 + 11x^4 + 7x - 8 - 5x^4 - 9x^3 + 3x - 4`

`= 2x^5 + 6x^4 - 9x^3 + 10x - 12`

### Method 2: Subtract vertically

```
   2x^5 + 11x^4 + 0x^3 + 7x - 8
-  0x^5 +  5x^4 + 9x^3 - 3x + 4
--------------------------------
   2x^5 +  6x^4 - 9x^3 + 10x - 12
```

